videos.description: Darnell Foreman electrifies Penn fans in the Palestra with a deep 3-pointer to beat the buzzer.
videos.headline: Quakers take lead at half on Foreman's buzzer-beater

videos.description: Justin Bassey gets the layup and the foul, and the Crimson bench is fired up.
videos.headline: Harvard bench loves Bassey's and-1

videos.description: Caleb Wood gives the Quakers a 3-point lead after draining a triple and getting the foul.
videos.headline: Wood extends Penn's lead with a 3

videos.description: Christian Juzang finds space beyond the arc and launches a 3-pointer to cut the deficit to 66-63 with under a minute left.
videos.headline: Juzang keeps Crimson alive with triple

videos.description: The Crimson were able to get a look off the inbound pass, but the Quakers earn a ticket to the tourney after 2 missed 3-pointers.
videos.headline: Penn's defense holds off Harvard at buzzer

videos.description: AJ Brodeur calls making the tournament a "dream come true" as the Quakers defeat Harvard 68-65 in the Palestra.
videos.headline: Penn punches ticket to 1st tournament in 10 years
